import { Avatar, Layout, Menu, DatePicker, Badge, Dropdown } from 'antd'
import './LandingPage.css'
import { BellOutlined, UserOutlined } from '@ant-design/icons'

export const LandingPage = () => {
  const { Header, Content, Footer } = Layout

  const menu = (
    <Menu>
      <Menu.Item>Profile</Menu.Item>
      <Menu.Item>Log Out</Menu.Item>
    </Menu>
  )

  return (
    <Layout>
      <Header>
        <Dropdown overlay={menu} placement='bottomLeft'>
          <Avatar className='avatar' icon={<UserOutlined />} />
        </Dropdown>
        <Menu className='ant-menu' mode='horizontal' defaultSelectedKeys={['1']}>
          <Menu.Item className='items'>Home</Menu.Item>
          <Menu.Item className='items'>Leaves</Menu.Item>
          <Menu.Item className='items'>Claims</Menu.Item>
          <Menu.Item className='items'>Payslips</Menu.Item>
        </Menu>
      </Header>
    </Layout>
  )
}
export default LandingPage
